<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로그인 | 갓생 업</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<main class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8 col-xl-6">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5">
                    <div class="text-center mb-4">
                        <p class="text-secondary text-uppercase small mb-2">Godsaeng Up</p>
                        <h1 class="h3 mb-2">로그인</h1>
                        <p class="text-body-secondary mb-0">아이디와 비밀번호로 계속 진행합니다.</p>
                    </div>

                    {{#param.error}}
                        <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                            로그인에 실패했습니다. 아이디와 비밀번호를 다시 확인해주세요.
                        </div>
                    {{/param.error}}

                    {{#param.logout}}
                        <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
                            로그아웃되었습니다.
                        </div>
                    {{/param.logout}}

                    <form method="post" action="/auth/login">
                        <input type="hidden" name="{{_csrf.parameterName}}" value="{{_csrf.token}}">

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="loginId" class="form-label">아이디</label>
                            <input id="loginId" type="text" name="loginId" class="form-control" placeholder="영문/숫자 4~20자" autocomplete="username" required>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label for="password" class="form-label">비밀번호</label>
                            <input id="password" type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요" autocomplete="current-password" required>
                        </div>

                        <div class="d-grid">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark">로그인</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>

                    <p class="text-center text-body-secondary mt-4 mb-0">
                        아직 계정이 없다면 <a href="/auth/register">회원가입</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
</body>
</html>
